### Compile (Linux)
1. Download source files  
`wget -q https://github.com/sophware/lyck/archive/master.zip -O /tmp/master.zip`  
`unzip -q /tmp/master.zip -d /tmp/`  
`cd /tmp/lyck-master`  

2. Compile  
  `make`

3. Set up USB Serial adapter  
http://www.panticz.de/USB-Serial-adapter

4. Run command  
`./lyc input dvd`  
`./lyc volume up`


